{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-006__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-006", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·006.1", "text_original": "天保定爾，亦孔之固。俾爾單厚，何福不除？俾爾多益，以莫不庶。", "text_normalized": "天保定爾，亦孔之固。俾爾單厚，何福不除？俾爾多益，以莫不庶。", "notes": "天保 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-006", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·006.2", "text_original": "天保定爾，俾爾戩穀。罄無不宜，受天百祿。降爾遐福，維日不足。", "text_normalized": "天保定爾，俾爾戩穀。罄無不宜，受天百祿。降爾遐福，維日不足。", "notes": "天保 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-006__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-006", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·006.3", "text_original": "天保定爾，以莫不興！如山如阜，如岡如陵。如川之方至，以莫不增。", "text_normalized": "天保定爾，以莫不興！如山如阜，如岡如陵。如川之方至，以莫不增。", "notes": "天保 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-006__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-006", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·006.4", "text_original": "吉蠲為饎，是用孝享。禴祠烝嘗，于公先王。君曰卜爾，萬壽無疆！", "text_normalized": "吉蠲為饎，是用孝享。禴祠烝嘗，于公先王。君曰卜爾，萬壽無疆！", "notes": "天保 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-006__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-006", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·006.5", "text_original": "神之弔矣，詒爾多福。民之質矣，日用飲食。羣黎百姓，徧為爾德。", "text_normalized": "神之弔矣，詒爾多福。民之質矣，日用飲食。羣黎百姓，徧為爾德。", "notes": "天保 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-006__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-006", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·006.6", "text_original": "如月之恆，如日之升。如南山之壽，不騫不崩。如松柏之茂，無不爾或承。", "text_normalized": "如月之恆，如日之升。如南山之壽，不騫不崩。如松柏之茂，無不爾或承。", "notes": "天保 Chinese stanza 6."}
